summary: Okay, so robots may have also gotten Chuck Wendig fired. I think we may have to seriously consider the robot uprising. Because...
body:
Okay, so robots may have also gotten Chuck Wendig fired.

I think we may have to seriously consider the robot uprising. Because if they become self aware, and realize how easy it is to get people fired, they will soon run everything.

Wait, is that really a bad thing?

title: You Spin Me Right Round
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2R4SVxg

by suckedintothesupermassive

Behind the suits and polished exterior of his businessman persona, Ben was really just a huge eighties nerd. He grew up with his parents playing the likes of David Bowie and Duran Duran constantly, whilst glued to his Nintendo.

Rey loved eighties music and movies but anyone who shared those interests was usually over the age of forty. So when Finn had told her that it was in fact an eighties themed party they would be attending, costumes expected, she was delighted, happy to partake in a rare Saturday night out.

Both fond of an era that didn’t belong to them, will these dorks find each other? Get your neon out and dancing shoes on - A Modern AU with eighties flair.

blog.description:
I'll come up with a better title eventually.

Short and sweet I'm a nerd/geek. I listen to punk. I'm a feminist. I'm an lgbtq ally. I'm a wanna be superhero/adventurer. Because I talk a lot about race and racism I should probably clarify that I’m white and male.?

One of the things I love is how speculative fiction can be used to talk about serious topics. Which is what this will mostly be about. Along with just some fun things.

blog.description: I am a descriptivist linguist for the Mando'a language. I show what it can do, not what it MUST do. This is a place for discussion about Mando'a, and Mandalorian society and culture. Feel free to use the head cannons from this blog (or reblogged from others) in your RP or writing. All words and descriptions are taken from the mandoa.org Mandalorian Dictionary. Want to support this blog? Buy me a Kofi? OR buy some Mando'a themed items? Visit our Discord? Blog icon by Rina
